Thuận tiện đi lại, cách trung tâm TP. HCM 15 phút di chuyển. Mọi chi tiết xin LH: A. Cường. Swanbay 57m corner apartment with the panoramic view from the apartment, has all conveniences and is fully furnished with premium interior and spacious bedroom - living room - bathroom - balcony for sale by homeowner. Located on Dai Phuoc island which offers a four - sided river view with refreshing breeze, the apartment is peaceful, safe, perfect for relaxation with all the modern amenities in residential area and on Swanbay island. (Especially there is an 18 - hole, par - 72 International standard golf course). Easy for commuting, only 15 minutes from Ho Chi Minh city center. For all details, please contact: Mr. Cuong. Đặc điểm nổi bật Diện tích : 57m2 Giá : 2,45 tỷ Phòng ngủ : 1 phòng Phòng tắm : 1 phòng
